{
  "stem": "11274.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she-- they stay in different buildings than we, already in Auschwitz I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they already had different buildings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had pillows, I think, and sheets and blankets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had just a straw-- straw-filled burlap sack and those beds, those bunk beds, and a thin blanket, like a rag over it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway, we're still together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they made us throw-- instead of carrying the blocks, they put us six to 10 feet apart, and throwing the blocks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you have to receive it with your hand till your hands were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was lasting till about September, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they-- one morning, we were lining up on roll call.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nobody ever told us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were just, like-- maybe they-- in the free world, you tell an animal more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some are directed, you're going this way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just marched out, and we kept on marching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not till they felt we marched the other direction, then-- and the field before, then the detail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in that other direction, we discovered when we came in, there were barracks there-- looked like stables.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were brick, too, but practically no windows there in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we marched in and assigned to different barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in the barracks were three-- three shelves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And a wall here and a wall here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the shelves, wooden planks, and a little rag of a blanket there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we started out with about six or so on one of those planks-- six on one, six on the second, six on the other one.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But then every single day, one more transport-- they march us out for details to work with the same kapo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The kapo moved to Auschwitz, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This was the men's camp, and they didn't have the other buildings ready.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
